If a [[Pyrovore]] is slain by a Wound that inflicted [[Instant Death]], it explodes, as per a vehicle that had suffered an ''Explodes!'' result on the Vehicle Damage Table, except that the hits are resolved at S 5 AP 2 (the same as its ''Acid Blood'' biomorph). Models with the [[Molten Body]] special rule or with the [[Acid Blood]] biomorph are unaffected by the explosion.